cat <(head -1507 0_nodoc.pos) <(cat 1_nodoc.pos) <(head -1480 2_nodoc.pos) <(head -1428 3_nodoc.pos) <(head -1584 4_nodoc.pos) > gold

Count empty lines
grep -cvP '\S' file
-P '\S'(perl regex) will match any line contains non-space
-v select non-matching lines
-c print a count of matching lines

cut -f1 gold > raw
